                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d964">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00116 European War 1939/427: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-08-26T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 26, 1941—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1000. Your 1545, August 20, 6 p.m.<note n="50" xml:id="d964fn50">Not
                        printed.</note> As a signatory of the Prisoners of War Convention of 1929,
                    not 1939,<note n="51" xml:id="d964fn51">This date had been used erroneously in
                        the Ambassador’s telegram to which reference is made.</note> and because of
                    its humanitarian interest in the treatment accorded prisoners of war, Department
                    is interested to learn whether the Soviet Government intends to observe this
                    convention. If the Soviet Government does not intend to observe the 1929 but
                    rather an earlier convention the Department would be equally interested to learn
                    of that fact. The Department would assume, of course, that the observation of
                    any such convention by the Soviet Government would be on a reciprocal basis as
                    indicated in the final paragraph of your 1458.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
